sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Cmd as artisan iae:sync-token
    participant Env as File .env
    participant SSO as iae-sso.virtualfri.id

    Dev->>Cmd: php artisan iae:sync-token
    Cmd->>Env: Baca IAE_API_KEY=KEY-MHS-117
    Cmd->>SSO: POST /api/v1/auth/token
    alt M2M key aktif
        SSO-->>Cmd: 200 token M2M
    else M2M 401 Unauthorized
        Cmd->>SSO: POST /api/v1/auth/token fallback warga01
        SSO-->>Cmd: 200 token user
    end
    Cmd->>Env: Tulis IAE_SSO_TOKEN + IAE_SSO_TOKEN_EXPIRES_AT
    Cmd-->>Dev: Token synced
